CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775473374
OL,3,CScientists identify trigger of Crohn's
OL,4,Cscarring, research suggests
OL,6,FCrohn's is a long-term, inflammatory
OL,7,Fcondition affecting the digestive
OL,8,Ftract and, over time, ongoing
OL,9,Finflammation can lead to fibrosis,
OL,10,Fwhere excess collagen builds up in the
OL,11,Fbowel wall.
OL,13,FThis scarring can cause the intestine
OL,14,Fto narrow and become blocked, meaning
OL,15,Fthat surgery is needed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
