PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775473374
OL,3,CScientists identify trigger of Crohn's
OL,4,Cscarring, research suggests
OL,6,FThe University of Edinburgh-led
OL,7,Fresearch team hope the latest findings
OL,8,Fcould help pinpoint therapeutic
OL,9,Ftargets that could be explored to
OL,10,Finterrupt the scarring process and
OL,11,Fdevelop treatments specifically aimed
OL,12,Fat fibrosis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
