FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775473374
OL,3,CScientists identify trigger of Crohn's
OL,4,Cscarring, research suggests
OL,6,FThe submucosa ` a deeper layer of the
OL,7,Fbowel wall ` had particularly high
OL,8,Flevels of scarring, indicating it may
OL,9,Fplay an important role in the early
OL,10,Fstages of fibrosis.
OL,12,FResearchers next analysed fresh
OL,13,Fintestinal tissue samples using a
OL,14,Fcutting-edge technique to study gene
OL,15,Factivity in individual cells, known as
OL,16,Fsingle-cell RNA sequencing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
