PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775473374
OL,3,CScientists identify trigger of Crohn's
OL,4,Cscarring, research suggests
OL,6,FThe research is published in The
OL,7,FJournal of Pathology.
OL,9,FIt was conducted by a UK-wide
OL,10,Fcollaboration of researchers and
OL,11,Fclinicians and was supported by
OL,12,Ffunding from the Leona M and Harry B
OL,13,FHelmsley Charitable Trust.
OL,15,FCatherine Winsor, director of service,
OL,16,Fresearch and evidence at the charity
OL,17,FCrohn's & Colitis UK, said: "People
OL,18,Fwho live with Crohn's often tell us
OL,19,Fhow much fibrosis and scarring can
OL,20,Faffect their lives, yet it's something
OL,21,Fcurrent treatments don't address.
OL,26,@yD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775473374
OL,3,CScientists identify trigger of Crohn's
OL,4,Cscarring, research suggests
OL,6,F"This early research is really
OL,7,Fexciting because it helps us to
OL,8,Funderstand what drives that scarring
OL,9,Fand where new treatments could make a
OL,10,Fdifference.
OL,12,F"It brings real hope that, in the
OL,13,Ffuture, we might be able to treat not
OL,14,Fjust inflammation, but the lasting
OL,15,Fdamage Crohn's can cause."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
